sections.Trivia:
- The brand of tea shown is Twinings.
- The names of the suspects come from "tea"[1]:
Juri Kosaka (高坂 樹理) comes from the café and tea chain Ginza Cozy Corner, commonly known as cozy (コージー ,kōjī?);
Tokie Happo (八方 時枝) comes from teapots (ポット ,potto?);
Katsuki Beppu (別府 華月) comes from teacups (カップ ,kappu?);
Reina Suto (須東 伶菜) comes from strainers (ストレーナー ,sutōrēnā?);
Tsuneo Suto (須東 恒夫) comes from boiling water (熱湯 ,nettō?);
Toji Kosaka (高坂 東治) comes from ceramics (陶磁器 ,tōjiki?).
